---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Astrobot.design | Web Design Agency"
  description="We build blazing fast websites for small businesses using AI-powered design and the Astro framework."
>
  <!-- Breadcrumb Navigation -->
  <nav class="py-4 border-b border-border/40">
    <div class="container text-sm text-muted-foreground">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">/</span>
      <a href="/about" class="text-foreground font-medium">About</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Building Websites That Perform</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-12">
          We're on a mission to prove that small businesses deserve fast, beautiful websites without the big agency price tag.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Story</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-muted-foreground text-lg">
          <p>
            Astrobot.design was founded on a simple observation: most small businesses have terrible websites. Not because their owners don't care, but because web design has become needlessly complicated and expensive.
          </p>
          <p>
            We started by combining two powerful tools: AI-powered design intelligence and the Astro framework. This combination lets us build beautiful, lightning-fast websites in days instead of months.
          </p>
          <p>
            Today, we help small business owners get online fast, rank higher in search results, and attract more customers without the typical 2-3 month timeline and five-figure price tag.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">⚡</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Speed-First Approach</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Every site we build is optimized for speed. We use the Astro framework to deliver sites that load 75% faster than traditional sites.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🤖</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">AI + Human Creativity</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We leverage AI intelligence to inform our design decisions, but never at the expense of human creativity and strategic thinking.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🎯</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Results-Focused</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Your website isn't just pretty—it's built to convert. Every design decision is made with your business goals in mind.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Our Philosophy</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Simple Over Complex</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We believe in clean, simple design and code. No unnecessary plugins, frameworks, or features cluttering your site.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Fast Is Non-Negotiable</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Speed isn't a nice-to-have—it's essential. Fast sites rank better in search, convert better, and provide a better user experience.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">Your Content Is King</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We design templates that showcase your content. Whether it's written copy, images, or videos, your content always takes center stage.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">SEO From Day One</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            SEO isn't an afterthought—it's built into every site from the beginning. Technical SEO, structured data, and mobile-first design are standard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Our Process</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="font-bold text-primary">1</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Discovery & Strategy</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                We start by understanding your business, goals, target audience, and unique value proposition. This guides every design decision.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="font-bold text-primary">2</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Design & Development</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                Our team creates a beautiful, functional design optimized for conversions. We build with Astro for maximum performance.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="font-bold text-primary">3</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Testing & Launch</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                Before going live, we test everything: speed, mobile responsiveness, browser compatibility, and SEO. You get a site that's ready to perform.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <span class="font-bold text-primary">4</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Growth & Support</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">
                After launch, we provide ongoing support, maintenance, and optimization to help your site grow and improve over time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 bg-muted/30">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">Technology We Use</h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Astro Framework</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">The fastest modern framework for building blazing-fast websites.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">TypeScript</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Type-safe code that's easier to maintain and less prone to errors.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Tailwind CSS</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Utility-first CSS for rapid, consistent design implementation.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-primary">✓</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Headless CMS</p>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Content management freedom without being tied to a specific framework.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Work With Us?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Let's discuss your project and see if we're the right fit.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
            Book a Consultation
          </a>
          <a href="/blog" class="border border-border px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-muted transition-colors">
            Read Our Blog
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
